extendedData.name: OracleText
extendedData.value:
With two ready-to-play sixty-card decks and exciting new cards from Core Set 2021, it's a great start to any collection and a wonderful introduction to the Magic community.
Contents:
• two 60 Card Decks
• 2 Quick-Start Guides
• 2 First Game Walk-Through Cards
• 1 "Rules and World of Magic" Booklet
• 1 MTG Arena Code Card*

name: Core Set 2021 Arena Starter Kit Amazon

extendedData.name: OracleText
extendedData.value:
Bundles are a great way for players to fully immerse themselves in the new set and update their decks for the new Standard environment. With plenty of lands and Draft Boosters, plus a life counter and reference cards, the Bundle also makes a great way for newer players to start building their decks.
Contents
• 10 boosters
• 1 storage box
• 20 premium lands and 20 normal lands
• 1 bundle promo card
• 1 oversized spindown counter
• 1 insert
